{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"@weknow/gatsby-remark-drupal","description":"Provides support for markdown preprocessing for Drupal body fields.","keywords":["drupal","gatsby","gatsby-plugin","markdown","remark"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"jmolivas","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/815e16aba0012405418d70909c06939b"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/weknowinc/gatsby-remark-drupal"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-remark-drupal\"><a href=\"#gatsby-remark-drupal\" aria-label=\"gatsby remark drupal permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-remark-drupal</h1>\n<p>Provides support for markdown preprocessing to Drupal body fields.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Creates a new <code class=\"language-text\">text/markdown</code> field for drupal body fields of the selected content types.</li>\n<li>Replaces Drupal relative image paths to previously downloaded and cached images by the <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-source-drupal</code> plugin.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOTE: To make sure your Drupal site expose markdown use the Toast UI Editor integration for Drupal provided by the <a href=\"https://www.drupal.org/project/tui_editor\">tui_editor</a> module.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save @weknow/gatsby-remark-drupal</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<h3 id=\"default-configuration\"><a href=\"#default-configuration\" aria-label=\"default configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Default configuration</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">      <span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`@weknow/gatsby-remark-drupal`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"custom-configuration\"><a href=\"#custom-configuration\" aria-label=\"custom configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Custom configuration</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">      <span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`@weknow/gatsby-remark-drupal`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              nodes<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`article`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`page`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`landing`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`cta`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-label=\"options permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options</h2>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Name</th>\n<th>Default</th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">nodes</code></td>\n<td>[<code class=\"language-text\">article</code>,<code class=\"language-text\">page</code>]</td>\n<td>The Drupal <code class=\"language-text\">node</code> types to process.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/@weknow/gatsby-remark-drupal/","id